creator: TONS GENERAL TRADING CO. W.L.L
descriptionHtml:
TONS deliver your groceries from local stores the same day.

Order from stores like Mishref Co-Op, Shamiya Co-Op, and Yarmouk Co-Op. Get your groceries delivered when you want them, the same day.

IT'S EASY AND FAST
Create a grocery order with a few taps. Our Personal Shoppers are experts at picking the best produce, meat and seafood. We will shop and deliver your order in as little as 1 hour! Save time and take back your nights and weekends!

● Order fresh produce picked just the way you like it
● Order from a variety departments and add items in your Favorites
● Schedule delivery for 2 hour from now or later in the week
● Keep an order history to help narrow your shopping list with a tap- Reorder previous items with one tap
● Save hours every week avoiding lines and parking and the supermarket

We serve all Governates depending on the store serving your area.

Your area not listed? We are working hard to service your area soon! Sign up now to be the first in your city to be notified when we launch!

Contact Us
We’d love to hear from you.
